"What do you call an 8 card suit?", and the answer is "Trumps" :). The point being that you really want to play in your 8 card suit. But, now lets take the bidding as is and see if Anna should bid 4 hearts or not. One thing she has going for her is the known 9 card fit. When stretching, you tend to be aggressive with a 9 card fit and unaggressive with an 8 card fit. |
