NT||cp|8|AT|^B@2^Z@3^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|In fact, if she finds the diamond return, they beat the hand with 2 spade ruffs, a heart ruff, and the CA. But that is not the reason to lead a spade. The reason is, it seems like the least likely to give away a trick. Heart would be my 2nd choice and it could very well be right on many hands.|
