NT||cp|8|AT|^B@2^Z@3^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|So, even if she made a responsive double (were we playing them) I probably still bid 3D. It turns out 4 hearts has plays, but it is far from cold, as Ann has to worry about doing something with all her clubs.|
